<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Certificat de formation</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f4f7fb;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#1f2937;">
    <div style="padding:32px 16px;background-color:#f4f7fb;">
        <div style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #dbe4f0;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;">
            <div style="background:#0f172a;padding:24px 28px;">
                <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;">
                    <tr>
                        {% if logo_cid %}
                            <td style="width:88px;vertical-align:middle;padding-right:16px;">
                                <div style="width:72px;height:72px;background:#ffffff;border-radius:18px;padding:8px;box-sizing:border-box;border:1px solid rgba(203,213,225,0.35);">
                                    <img src="{{ logo_cid }}" alt="HR One" style="display:block;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:contain;border:0;">
                                </div>
                            </td>
                        {% endif %}
                        <td style="vertical-align:middle;">
                            <div style="font-size:24px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.2;color:#ffffff;">HR One</div>
                            <div style="margin-top:6px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;color:#cbd5e1;">Certificat de formation</div>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>

            <div style="padding:28px;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 18px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;">
                    Bonjour <strong>{{ participant_name }}</strong>,
                </p>

                <p style="margin:0 0 24px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#475569;">
                    Votre certificat pour la formation <strong>{{ formation_title }}</strong> est pret. Vous le trouverez en piece jointe a cet e-mail.
                </p>

                <div style="background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #dbe4f0;border-radius:14px;padding:20px 22px;">
                    <div style="margin-bottom:14px;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;">
                        {{ formation_title }}
                    </div>

                    <div style="margin-bottom:8px;font-size:14px;color:#334155;">
                        <strong>Mode :</strong> {{ formation_mode }}
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom:8px;font-size:14px;color:#334155;">
                        <strong>Niveau :</strong> {{ formation_level }}
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom:8px;font-size:14px;color:#334155;">
                        <strong>Date debut :</strong> {{ formation_start }}
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom:8px;font-size:14px;color:#334155;">
                        <strong>Date fin :</strong> {{ formation_end }}
                    </div>
                    <div style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;">
                        <strong>Date emission :</strong> {{ issued_at }}
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p style="margin:24px 0 0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#475569;">
                    Le certificat PDF est joint a ce message.<br>
                    <strong>Equipe HR One</strong>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
